<p>Weirdly named <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/gnome-backgrounds/-/blob/gnome-45/backgrounds/morphogenesis-l.svg?ref_type=heads">Morphogenesis</a> is one of my favorite additions this release. Based around a concept of reactive diffusion, described by none other than <a href="https://www.dna.caltech.edu/courses/cs191/paperscs191/turing.pdf">Allan Turing</a>, features a little easter egg if you’re into chasing those down.</p>

